&lt;p&gt;Do you need a better work/life balance? Opportunities have arisen to recruit additional experienced Housekeeping assistants to our Temporary Staffing Bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To work as part of a team performing cleaning and housekeeping duties in clinical, non clinical and public areas of the premises. The post holder is expected to meet the National Specifications for Cleanliness in the NHS, maintaining cleaning and housekeeping standards.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Previous experience would be an advantage, but full training will be provided for all post holders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The benefits of working on our Staff Bank are:-&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;* Choice of available shifts&lt;br /&gt;* Paid annual leave entitlement&lt;br /&gt;* Weekly pay&lt;br /&gt;* NHS Pension&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This advert may be closed earlier to the closing date if sufficient number of applicants apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held 30th November - 4th December&lt;/p&gt;
